rows.label: tlk41200122_03_msg0001
rows.name:
Whee, it's time to feed the Armoo!
Their food's got a healthy balance
of nutrition!

rows.label: tlk41200122_03_msg0002
rows.name:
Armoo're herbivores, but they don't
just eat grass all day, nope!

rows.label: tlk41200122_03_msg0003
rows.name:
They need to trim their teeth down
on Ruby Mangosteens and they
need vitamins from Deadly Kiwis!

rows.label: tlk41200122_03_msg0004
rows.name: Does it sound like hard work?

rows.label: tlk41200122_03_msg0005
rows.name:
Mmm, I don't mind. 'Cos I wuv my
wittle Armoo, yes I do!
